### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("jwt", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Listar inventario (paginado, scope tenant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Crear item de inventario (referencia a perfil o item)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profileId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "itemId": null,
  "quantity": 150.00,
  "location": "Almacen A - Estante 12",
  "costPriceEur": 98.50,
  "supplier": "Aceros Martinez SL",
  "notes": "Lote 2026-001"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("invId", response.body.id);
%}

### Obtener item de inventario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory/{{invId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Actualizar item de inventario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory/{{invId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 99.00,
  "location": "Almacen B - Estante 5",
  "costPriceEur": 95.00,
  "supplier": "Aceros Martinez SL",
  "notes": "Ajuste por inventario fisico"
}

### Eliminar item de inventario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory/{{invId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
